       Property Tax Assistance For Blind, Disabled or Senior Citizens
   title bar

                                                                         *

   The State of California administers two programs to assist low-income
   blind, disabled or senior citizens pay property taxes. The following
   programs have maximum income levels and have different provisions

     * Property Tax Postponement
     * Homeowner And Renter Assistance







